{"tid":1200574,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"原來交通擁擠嘅成因好撚簡單","createTime":"2019-06-10T18:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T02:07:07.000Z","uid":5477,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0a6a14bb18b7a2a429d8b4ee0c5dd739a136a9c5","tid":1200574,"uid":5477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:53:46.000Z","msg":"學術討論：學界有一個橫跨物理學、生物學、數學、電腦科學、社會科學等等的範疇，叫做複雜系統(complex system)。<br />\n<br />\n其中一個研究題目，就是交通擠塞的成因。研究指，只要有極少數的車輛，突發、急劇地改變車速(如動畫中的紅色車輛)，就會引發連鎖效應，導致系統性的擠塞。<br />\n<br />\n即使是極偶然而微小的力量，也可以引發牽連大波。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iHzzSao6ypE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiHzzSao6ypE&d=bDeBUyUVyPRGeZhx3zx6lZnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=96e7b0b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iHzzSao6ypE</a>"},{"pid":"50c26b00a35d1e0c39491885e266c21898308147","tid":1200574,"uid":5477,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:56:55.000Z","msg":"原來急剎車同經常轉線就可以造成擠塞，個個都咁做中區咪仆街，千祈唔好學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acdf2839660bf9207258339d86abd83274e5a6ed","tid":1200574,"uid":232594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"50c26b00a35d1e0c39491885e266c21898308147","tid":1200574,"uid":5477,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T18:56:55.000Z","msg":"原來急剎車同經常轉線就可以造成擠塞，個個都咁做中區咪仆街，千祈唔好學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T19:10:58.000Z","msg":"架車自己失靈就冇計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e3cc1ef76aed610542c5cb2b485adcdd05279d","tid":1